      "description": "The [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} babbles incoherently while it doesn't have the Incapacitated condition.\n\nWisdom Saving Throw: DC [[lookup @save.dc.value activity=PyGOI84k0PPYrru8]], any [[lookup @target.affects.type activity=PyGOI84k0PPYrru8]] that starts its turn within [[lookup @target.template.size activity=PyGOI84k0PPYrru8]] feet of the [[lookup @name lowercase]]{monster} while it is babbling.\n\nFailure: The target rolls [[/r 1d8]] to determine what it does during the current turn:\n\n1\u20134. The target does nothing.\n\n5\u20136. The target takes no action or Bonus Action and uses all its movement to move in a random direction.\n\n7\u20138. The target makes a melee attack against a randomly determined creature within its reach or does nothing if it can't make such an attack.",
